I have a lot of friends who are able to stay in active relationships even

00:00:03.850 --> 00:00:06.850
 when they're deployed overseas.  So one of my friends for instance

00:00:06.850 --> 00:00:09.850
 like a nice way that he gets to keep up with his girlfriend is that

00:00:09.850 --> 00:00:12.850
 she sends him letters or like care packages that have like his favorite

00:00:12.850 --> 00:00:15.850
 candy bars and food and like a nice note inside of it.  Sometimes

00:00:15.850 --> 00:00:18.850
 she even flies out to where the ship docks, so like they just landed

00:00:18.850 --> 00:00:21.850
 in Rota Spain and so she had a fun trip out to Spain to go see

00:00:21.850 --> 00:00:24.850
 him.

